rows.label: qst001903_msg0002
rows.name: Oh... The job I gave to Sokoko...

rows.label: qst001903_msg0003
rows.name:
You managed to do it, did ya?
Not bad going.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0004
rows.name:
The little furball gave up?
Not surprised.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0005
rows.name: I did my best to explain it.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0006
rows.name:
It wasn't a job for your everyday
salvager. Needs a Blade, really.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0007
rows.name:
But that little clump o' fluff wouldn't
listen to reason.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0008
rows.name:
"Mushroom-Feast Salvager Sokoko
salvage anything, meh-meh-meh!"
...The daft wee thing...

rows.label: qst001903_msg0009
rows.name:
Gotta admire that can-do Nopon
attitude though.

rows.label: qst001903_msg0010
rows.name:
Well, I guess I'd better give you the
reward.
